{"tid":1369673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果元朗呢步棋會唔會行錯左","createTime":"2019-07-26T18:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T22:40:34.000Z","uid":76398,"like":1,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4e2bc0875607d4aa0d1f398dada90e4e5bb9785d","tid":1369673,"uid":76398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:11:42.000Z","msg":"想像下，假如今個星期六日變成包圍政總遊行，以現時氣氛，好大機會係過百萬嘅級數，無論輿論壓力，國際上嘅曝光，甚至想衝時嘅支援，都應該相當可觀。連政府內部都出現倒戈，勇武響政總可以放心做<br />\n<br />\n相比好多和理非人會有顧忌唔去，敵人未必出現，當地街坊主流談唔上係同伴，無沙田咁多幫手嘅元朗行山，既未必打擊到白衫敵人，同時都無將恐怖襲擊spin向中港共嘅效果<br />\n<br />\n雖然情感上我都想覆桌，但可能真係有比元朗更好嘅野可以做，不過事到如今都無得番轉頭，聽日元朗見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf12c0de63c001812a43588075f97988958198a","tid":1369673,"uid":10524,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:12:53.000Z","msg":"728 都係大戰"},{"pid":"da2cbb6acf7993def90e85b2b8039914a07cdacd","tid":1369673,"uid":227929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:12:58.000Z","msg":"728港島遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5021728c0428cbcc1a704368b933216da6266d74","tid":1369673,"uid":51250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:13:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3153ba1eef35fc05a85994beb9db45131051ed","tid":1369673,"uid":76398,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"3bf12c0de63c001812a43588075f97988958198a","tid":1369673,"uid":10524,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:12:53.000Z","msg":"728 都係大戰"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:15:48.000Z","msg":"但同元朗幾乎重疊，動員上好明顯跟唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d548896d950e852252795be56676777ad9c20d4a","tid":1369673,"uid":226959,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:17:16.000Z","msg":"